Hi guys!! @a.v.l.a and I are doing an AIRPODS giveaway to say thank you for helping us reach 11k subscribers on youtube before the end of the year! 🤩
To enter the giveaway: 
1️⃣ Subscribe to our Youtube channel: Isaac & Andrea (link in bio) 
2️⃣ Like & comment on videos 
3️⃣ Must be following @a.v.l.a and @isaac.cervantes 
4️⃣ Turn on your post notifications so you don’t miss any videos! 
5️⃣ Comment when done! 
6️⃣ TAG friends or share this to your story for extra entries 
We’ll be announcing the winner at 12k subscribers ☺️ Good luck!
